# Files Cloudflare Pages/Workers should NOT upload as static assets.
# The mirror keeps these in the repo; they're just excluded from deploy.
#
# Cloudflare Pages caps a single asset at 25 MiB. This video is 27.3 MiB, so it
# can't be served by Pages until it's compressed under 25 MiB or moved to
# external hosting (YouTube / Cloudflare Stream / R2). Until then it's skipped;
# the <video> on partyentertainment.html will show its poster but not play.
